summary:
This file is for those that dont want to update skyrim but want to run a mod for higher versions!
 This will fix your title screen chashes...
descriptionHtml:
Do you have a slow connection, or just dont want to wait skyrim update, but want use a mod that requires higher versions, this is for you!
 NOTES:
-I\'ve only tested on my 1.1.21 version, I\'m not sure about 1.0
-Some mods will not work fine (some REALLY requires content from the updates)
-I\'ll not support anything.

Example:
If you tried to run Dovahkiin Relaxes or fLokii static DOF  in version 1.1.21, and result in crash on start screen, this will fix it =P
author: Maxxius
